data.description: Heart of Bella Vista!Nestled in the trees offering beautiful view off the deck and next to bike trails! Would be a great Airbnb or VRBO. The Convenience of this Home Counts!Basically in the heart of Bella Vista…close to almost everything dining, country clubs, shopping, medical, gas stations, banks + more! New flooring in living room with a Cathedral ceiling opens up the space even more. Brick fireplace to snuggle up to! French doors to the back. Flat driveway…YAY…!!! Ceramic tile entry leading into large living room with the fireplace as a focal point. All the rooms are nice sized. Bella Vista has so much to offer with Trails=mountain biking and regular biking plus walking, Branchwood Recreation center has a concrete path meandering through the trees, more recreation centers with gathering areas, swimming pools, playgrounds, golfing, tennis, exercise areas, indoor pool, saunas and whirlpools, playgrounds, covered pavilions, lakes that offer great fishing for bass, crappie, walleye, perch, catfish and so much more!
